name: Bifrost
description:
Inspired by 80s synthwave vibe, I recorded this tracks using analog synthesizers and some drum samples. All the patches was designed by me and tuned to A=432hz for a different experience. For the covers did some basic coding on hydra.

This is the last piece of my EP "pixelate" 5/5.
It called "Bifrost". Recorded in A=432hz
I'm glad to finish this work, i hope you all enjoy my synth sounds.

Gear for this track
Korg Minilogue - synth
SSL2+ - audiobox
Ableton Live 11
